T02TD3388E:55b-1: ma h'a ba la s'a dha nam /
T02TD3388E:55b-4: bcom ldan 'das stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3388E:55b-5: sngon du bstan pa'i chogs stong pa nyid du bsgoms pa'i rjes su padma dkar po dang /
T02TD3388E:55b-6: nyi ma la h'um las bskyed pa'i stobs po che zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
T02TD3388E:55b-7: yan lag thams cad dmar po /
T02TD3388E:55b-8: skra kham pa gyen du bgreng ba /
T02TD3388E:55b-10: phyag g-yas kyi dang po na dbyug pa dkar po bsnams pa /
T02TD3388E:55b-11: g-yas kyi gnyis pa na rnga yab dkar po bsnams pa /
T02TD3388E:55b-12: phyag g-yon gyi dang po na phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul du byed pa'i phyag go //
T02TD3388E:55b-13: g-yon gyi phyag gnyis pa na sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa'o //
T02TD3388E:55b-14: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02TD3388E:55b-15: sprul gyi rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan cing mdzes pa /
T02TD3388E:55b-17: zhal mche ba gcig pa gnyis ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od kyi phreng ba dang ldan pa /
T02TD3388E:55b-18: dam tshig sems dpar bdag nyid rdzogs par byas la /
T02TD3388E:55b-19: ye shes sems dpa' dang gcig tu byas la /
T02TD3388E:55b-20: 'od dpag med pas dbu brgyan par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3388E:55b-21: de nas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3388E:55b-23: aom ma h'a ba la sv'a h'a zhes bya'o //
T02TD3388E:56a-2: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3388E:56a-3: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur cing zhus so //
